query:
SELECT X.CARRIER_SERIAL_NUM , NULL QTY ,
 CASE WHEN ( ( x.CH0A1 = Y.CH0A1)   AND 
             ( x.CH1A1 = Y.CH1A1)   AND
             ( x.CH2A1 = Y.CH2A1)   AND
             ( x.CH3A1 = Y.CH3A1)   AND
( x.CH0A2 = Y.CH0A2)   AND 
             ( x.CH1A2 = Y.CH1A2)   AND
             ( x.CH2A2 = Y.CH2A2)   AND
             ( x.CH3A2 = Y.CH3A2)   AND
( x.CH0A3 = Y.CH0A3)   AND 
             ( x.CH1A3 = Y.CH1A3)   AND
             ( x.CH2A3 = Y.CH2A3)   AND
             ( x.CH3A3 = Y.CH3A3)   AND
( x.CH0AM1 = Y.CH0AM1)   AND 
             ( x.CH1AM1 = Y.CH1AM1)   AND
             ( x.CH2AM1 = Y.CH2AM1)   AND
             ( x.CH3AM1 = Y.CH3AM1)   AND
( x.CH0LR = Y.CH0LR)   AND 
             ( x.CH1LR = Y.CH1LR)   AND
             ( x.CH2LR = Y.CH2LR)   AND
             ( x.CH3LR = Y.CH3LR)   AND
( x.VSTDMC = Y.VSTDMC)  AND   
( x.VSTDM = Y.VSTDM )   
            
            )  THEN 'IGUAL' ELSE 'DIFFERENT' END STATUS, NULL CH0A1 ,NULL CH1A1  , NULL CH2A1 , NULL CH3A1 , NULL CH0A2 ,NULL CH1A2  ,NULL CH2A2 ,NULL CH3A2 , NULL CH0A3  ,NULL CH1A3 ,NULL CH2A3 ,NULL  CH3A3  ,NULL CH0AM1 ,NULL CH1AM1 , NULL CH2AM1, NULL  CH3AM1 ,
           NULL    CH0LR  ,NULL CH1LR ,NULL CH2LR , NULL CH3LR  ,NULL VSTDMC  ,NULL VSTDM
 from

(SELECT carrier_Serial_num, 'MS' REVISION,   Count(case when a.part_num = '283VSCH0A1' then 1 end) CH0A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A1'then 1 END) CH1A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A1'then 1 end )CH2A1,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A1'then 1 end )CH3A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A2'then 1 end) CH0A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A2'then 1 end) CH1A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A2'then 1 end) CH2A2,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A2'then 1 end) CH3A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A3'then 1 end) CH0A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A3'then 1 end) CH1A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A3'then 1 end) CH2A3,
Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A3'then 1 end) CH3A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0AM1'then 1 end)CH0AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1AM1'then 1 end) CH1AM1,

 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2AM1'then 1 end) CH2AM1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3AM1'then 1 end) CH3AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0LR'then 1 end) CH0LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1LR'then 1 end) CH1LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2LR'then 1 end) CH2LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3LR'then 1 end) CH3LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDMC'then 1 end) VSTDMC,  Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDM'then 1 end) VSTDM 
       FROM phase2.part_info A, phase2.carrier_site b WHERE a.serial_num IN( 
 SELECT serial_num  FROM PHASE2.CARRIER_SITE where CARRIER_SERIAL_NUM IN (  'P834889'
 )
 )
 and a.serial_num = b.serial_num 
 AND B.STATUS = 'AVAIL' 
 GROUP BY carrier_serial_num   )x,


 (SELECT carrier_Serial_num,   'PA' REVISION,    Count(case when a.part_num = '283VSCH0A1' then 1 end) CH0A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A1'then 1 END) CH1A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A1'then 1 end )CH2A1,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A1'then 1 end )CH3A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A2'then 1 end) CH0A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A2'then 1 end) CH1A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A2'then 1 end) CH2A2,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A2'then 1 end) CH3A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A3'then 1 end) CH0A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A3'then 1 end) CH1A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A3'then 1 end) CH2A3,
Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A3'then 1 end) CH3A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0AM1'then 1 end)CH0AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1AM1'then 1 end) CH1AM1,



 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2AM1'then 1 end) CH2AM1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3AM1'then 1 end) CH3AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0LR'then 1 end) CH0LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1LR'then 1 end) CH1LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2LR'then 1 end) CH2LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3LR'then 1 end) CH3LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDMC'then 1 end) VSTDMC,  Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDM'then 1 end) VSTDM 
       FROM phase2.part_info@phase2 A, phase2.carrier_site@phase2 b WHERE a.serial_num IN( 
 SELECT serial_num  FROM PHASE2.CARRIER_SITE@phase2 where CARRIER_SERIAL_NUM IN (  'P834889'
 )
 )
 and a.serial_num = b.serial_num 
 AND B.STATUS = 'AVAIL' 
 GROUP BY carrier_serial_num ) y

 WHERE x.carrier_serial_num = y.carrier_serial_num




        UNION ALL


  SELECT  carrier_Serial_num, Count (*) QTY, 'MS' REVISION,    Count(case when a.part_num = '283VSCH0A1' then 1 end) CH0A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A1'then 1 END) CH1A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A1'then 1 end )CH2A1,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A1'then 1 end )CH3A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A2'then 1 end) CH0A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A2'then 1 end) CH1A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A2'then 1 end) CH2A2,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A2'then 1 end) CH3A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A3'then 1 end) CH0A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A3'then 1 end) CH1A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A3'then 1 end) CH2A3,
Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A3'then 1 end) CH3A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0AM1'then 1 end)CH0AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1AM1'then 1 end) CH1AM1,

 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2AM1'then 1 end) CH2AM1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3AM1'then 1 end) CH3AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0LR'then 1 end) CH0LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1LR'then 1 end) CH1LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2LR'then 1 end) CH2LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3LR'then 1 end) CH3LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDMC'then 1 end) VSTDMC,  Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDM'then 1 end) VSTDM 
       FROM phase2.part_info A, phase2.carrier_site b WHERE a.serial_num IN( 
 SELECT serial_num  FROM PHASE2.CARRIER_SITE where CARRIER_SERIAL_NUM IN (  'P834889'
 )
 )
 and a.serial_num = b.serial_num 
 AND B.STATUS = 'AVAIL' 
 GROUP BY carrier_serial_num  

 UNION ALL


 SELECT carrier_Serial_num,Count(*) QTY,   'PA' REVISION,   Count(case when a.part_num = '283VSCH0A1' then 1 end) CH0A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A1'then 1 END) CH1A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A1'then 1 end )CH2A1,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A1'then 1 end )CH3A1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A2'then 1 end) CH0A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A2'then 1 end) CH1A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A2'then 1 end) CH2A2,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A2'then 1 end) CH3A2,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0A3'then 1 end) CH0A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1A3'then 1 end) CH1A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2A3'then 1 end) CH2A3,
Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3A3'then 1 end) CH3A3,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0AM1'then 1 end)CH0AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1AM1'then 1 end) CH1AM1,



 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2AM1'then 1 end) CH2AM1, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3AM1'then 1 end) CH3AM1,Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH0LR'then 1 end) CH0LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH1LR'then 1 end) CH1LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH2LR'then 1 end) CH2LR, Count(case when part_num ='283VSCH3LR'then 1 end) CH3LR,
 Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDMC'then 1 end) VSTDMC,  Count(case when part_num ='283VSTDM'then 1 end) VSTDM 
       FROM phase2.part_info@phase2 A, phase2.carrier_site@phase2 b WHERE a.serial_num IN( 
 SELECT serial_num  FROM PHASE2.CARRIER_SITE@phase2 where CARRIER_SERIAL_NUM IN (  'P834889'
 )
 )
 and a.serial_num = b.serial_num 
 AND B.STATUS = 'AVAIL' 
 GROUP BY carrier_serial_num
